ollow&quot;>\r\n                Direct investment            <\/a>\r\n        <\/h3>\r\n                        <p>\r\n            Berkshire Consulting invests directly in renewable energy projects such as wind farms, solar farms, or hydroelectric power plants. These investments can provide the company with a direct stake in the revenue generated by the project.        <\/p>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-8bd5c32\" data-id=\"8bd5c32\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1ecba60 elementor-widget elementor-widget-creote-content-box-v1\" data-id=\"1ecba60\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"creote-content-box-v1.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t    \r\n<div class=\"content_box_cn  style_one\"\r\n     data-aos=\"fade-up\"  data-aos-offset=\"0\"\r\n    data-aos-delay=\"0\" >\r\n                <div class=\"txt_content\">\r\n                <h3>\r\n            <a href=\"\"  target=&quot;_blank&quot;                 rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;>\r\n                Equity investments            <\/a>\r\n        <\/h3>\r\n                        <p>\r\n            The company may invest in the equity of renewable energy companies that are publicly traded or privately held. This investment provides Berkshire Consulting with a stake in the company's earnings, and potentially benefit from any growth in the value of the company.        <\/p>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-fdb0cba\" data-id=\"fdb0cba\" data-element_type=\"colu